AddEvent - Class in blue.mdc.event
Add Event class create a pane and adds text fields to the pane asking for: Event Name Organization Name Advisor Transportation Number of Students in Organization Number of Students attending event Number of chaperones attending event Start Date and End Date Location Also it has a SAVE button to save the information to the database
AddEvent() - Constructor for class blue.mdc.event.AddEvent
 
AddTraveler - Class in blue.mdc.event
Add Traveler class create a pane and adds text fields to the pane asking for: Name Last Name MDC IDC Phone Email Address City Campus Zip Code Also it has a button to add contact information of the student, and a NEXT button to save and proceed to fill the EmergencyContact information to the database.
AddTraveler() - Constructor for class blue.mdc.event.AddTraveler
Constructor to AddTraveler to the the MainView.
